# Higgsfield AI Credentials
# API key mode: set HF_API_KEY + HF_SECRET (from https://cloud.higgsfield.ai/api-keys)
# Clerk mode: set HF_EMAIL + HF_PASSWORD (your normal account)
# Clerk mode takes priority when both are set.

HF_API_KEY=
HF_SECRET=

# Uncomment and fill in for Clerk (email/password) mode:
# HF_EMAIL=your.email@example.com
# HF_PASSWORD=your_password